4:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門人答你：行下新開賭場同食下野就冇架啦<br />\n不過水舞間堅好睇，野食太多有冇價錢限定？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個啲咩燈塔同教堂伏唔伏？"},{"pid":"32623e11a2e7047ad873df14c9949fff857fdc02","tid":19381,"uid":7677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73c361a2cc1daad8474107e763f7876965f5aa7d","tid":19381,"uid":50436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"巴黎人鐵塔上唔上39樓個觀景台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42f55300d644601d5886f7af9197a34608237aa","tid":19381,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:45:20.000Z","msg":"松山公園搭纜車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcbad1ed37b1e774760d4101b6910cdaa6074f6","tid":19381,"uid":2226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"咩時間去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063816719a84040ddb7ac4152c7f2b3768aae256","tid":19381,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>澳門人答你：行下新開賭場同食下野就冇架啦<br />\n不過水舞間堅好睇，野食太多有冇價錢限定？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個啲咩燈塔同教堂伏唔伏？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己呢世人應該都只係去左二，三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都唔知"},{"pid":"71e0c6b07fe893b700e6838eb069ea293740da08","tid":19381,"uid":2212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴黎人鐵塔上唔上39樓個觀景台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除非你住巴黎人包埋(我包7樓加$20每人可以上埋去)，否則要比百幾蚊上就算吧喇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/121403_c05917282da5d115a24036f9ec33aee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F121403_c05917282da5d115a24036f9ec33aee9.jpg&h=75fe9dc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c12becb1e5caa3e755b70c43d7d5547193e4a9a","tid":19381,"uid":38906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>澳門人答你：行下新開賭場同食下野就冇架啦<br />\n不過水舞間堅好睇，野食太多有冇價錢限定？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個啲咩燈塔同教堂伏唔伏？</blockquote><br />\n教堂伏到不行，港女自拍聖地"},{"pid":"68d4227e8fae1ad62bfffc669740eba134f63e3e","tid":19381,"uid":38906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"你去下載個金光飛航app，入面有個特別優惠買飛會平好多，水舞間好Q貴，有錢先去<br />\n如果真係要住，就過珠海住7天沃爾瑪分店啦<br />\n其實澳門無咩好行，如果2日trip，我會一日澳門行，夜晚過珠海食晚餐，訓一晚珠海摩爾廣場食韓國炸雞同海底撈，再去揚名廣場食韓國芝士排骨同汕頭牛肉<br />\n利申∶因為工作需要，經常要去澳門同珠海"},{"pid":"86ed8166d4cba21aea8394e8dbf95e7a2abef76a","tid":19381,"uid":18130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"去三盞燈囉"},{"pid":"b89c019cc6f5cc9dbbe1a80227f3d18300d680a3","tid":19381,"uid":50436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你去下載個金光飛航app，入面有個特別優惠買飛會平好多，水舞間好Q貴，有錢先去<br />\n如果真係要住，就過珠海住7天沃爾瑪分店啦<br />\n其實澳門無咩好行，如果2日trip，我會一日澳門行，夜晚過珠海食晚餐，訓一晚珠海摩爾廣場食韓國炸雞同海底撈，再去揚名廣場食韓國芝士排骨同汕頭牛肉<br />\n利申∶因為工作需要，經常要去澳門同珠海</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我book左巴黎人酒店lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都係貪佢新 澳門套票相隔一個禮拜就加左百幾二百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖誕去"},{"pid":"301fba77d3fae5fa9f06282bcc85de8c9f2fd155","tid":19381,"uid":50436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩時間去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n28/12 去 澳門哩啲日子有乜挽"},{"pid":"cd0100a477a36726dd2ccd4ef0f6a229c13d131c","tid":19381,"uid":50436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>松山公園搭纜車<i